    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1874-06-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1874-06-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="263" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d263">
                <head>No. 562.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cushing</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1874-06-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 1, 1874</date>.
                                (Received June 22.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 21.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to report that my
                            official presentation to the President of the executive power of the
                            Spanish republic took place on Saturday, the 30th ultimo, according to
                            the usual forms practiced in Spain.</p>
                <p>I am, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C. CUSHING.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
